  	<script type="text/javascript">

  	let content = {
  		Material_Spiritual_Converging: "The spiritual realm adds depth and meaning to the material object while the "+ "material allows expression of the spiritual realm by being its conduit or physical embodiment. A material-spiritual convergence is greater than its individual separate parts.<br /> Like steel reinforcing "+ "concrete. The steel gives flexibility to the concrete and the concrete gives strength to the steel.<br /><br /><strong>Examples of Spiritual & Material Converging</strong>: "+
