          	"<li><strong>incorruptible</strong>: beyond reproach or needs no justification -- holy text, animal instict, or Satan itself</li>"+
              "<li><strong>intangible</strong>: can't be held or touched. Has no physical presence</li>"+
          	"<li><strong>genuine</strong>: corroborates with what the mind knows it should be and what the thing actually is</li>"+ 
